#

Tofu Lettuce Wraps

25 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick

Description

Fresh, crunchy lettuce wraps filled with savory tofu and veggies, perfect for a light meal!

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • lettuce leaves: 1 head (Butter or Romaine)
  • bell pepper: 1 (diced)
  • carrot: 1 (grated)
  • green onion: 2 (sliced)
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • sesame oil: 1 tbsp
  • garlic: 2 cloves (minced)
  • ginger: 1 tsp (grated)
  • sesame seeds: 1 tbsp (optional)
